snippet.title: Super Cat Tales 2 - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW on iOS and Android!

iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/super-cat-tales-2/id1415392812

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neutronized.supercattales2


New mobile game adventure Super Cat Tales returns with an incredible new mobile game adventure! Cat heroes in action in a fantastic new mobile platformer game.

A mysterious army of tin soldiers has invaded Neko land and it's up to Alex and his friends to stop the evil plans of Lord Iridium.

Lord Iridium and his tin army is after a precious mineral that will make them indestructible, it is said this legendary mineral also grants equilibrium to Neko land and the entire planet. Will Alex and his friends be able to stop Lord Iridium before it's too late?

Coming 2018.

Follow @Neutronized for updates.
